summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting deeds to portion of the northwest one-quarter of Section 27, Township 24 North, Range 4 portion of Government Lot 3 in Section 34, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M., portion Block 18, Lake Side City Addition, portion of Government Lot 3 in Section 34, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M. and portion on the southwest one-quarter Section 29, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., for street purposes and laying of South Holly Street (33rd Avenue South Sanitary Sewer Project); 39th Avenue Northeast and 36th Avenue South (Miscellaneous street dedications); and North 106th Street (Rezone Petition - C.F. 284504).
